high_descs: Walk along the brick-walled hallway, the stand behind the shelf at the end of the shelf.
Pick up the white pencil that is on the wooden tray on the shelf.
Take the pen to the bedroom behind you, and go to the desk.
Put the pencil on the desk.
Walk around the foot of the bed and go into the bathroom near the sink of the bed.
Pick up the pencil that is in the sink.
Take that pen to the desk in the bedroom you were just in.
Put that pencil on the desk behind the first pen.
anns.task_desc: Take two pencils to the desk in the bedroom.

high_descs: Turn around and go near the shelf.

Take another pencil from the sink.
Turn around and go to the desk in the bedroom.
Put the pencil on the desk.

high_descs: Head rotate and turn left to the shelf.
